Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.42,0:00:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,他们非常高大，有时身高2米以上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They're quite large. Seven feet tall is not unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.76,0:00:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,动作很快，非常强壮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They're extremely fast and strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.05,0:00:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,上尉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.81,0:00:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,别犯错，他们可能会非常危险\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Make no mistake, they can be highly dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.81,0:00:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,科普兰人的基本武器：科里镖\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The Capellan's basic weapon: The kligat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.65,0:00:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,100米以内\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}At any distance up to 100 yards,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.65,0:00:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,足以抗衡手持相位枪的人类\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}they can make it almost as effective against a man as a phaser.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.57,0:00:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,除此之外，还有各种类型的剑和刀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In addition to this, an assortment of swords and knives.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.41,0:00:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,舰桥发来的，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Call from the Bridge, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.99,0:00:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,舰桥，我是舵手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bridge. Helm, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.83,0:00:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,收到，苏鲁先生请讲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, Mr. Sulu. Report.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.08,0:00:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,现在处于标准轨道，已经锁定他们的营房\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now in standard orbit, sir. I've pinpointed their encampment below.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.04,0:00:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,很好，准备好传送室\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Very good. Have the Transporter Room stand by.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.46,0:00:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Aye, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.51,0:00:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你在这个星球驻扎多久了，医生？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How long were you stationed on the planet, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.93,0:00:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,几个月而已\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Only a few months.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.30,0:00:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我们发现他们对医疗援助完全没有兴趣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We found them totally uninterested in medical aid or hospitals.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.85,0:00:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,他们认为强者才能生存下来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They believe that only the strong should survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.27,0:00:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,各位有什么看法？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Analysis, gentlemen?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.85,0:01:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,一般在这种情况下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ordinarily, under these circumstances,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.94,0:01:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我会建议派遣大量武装人员登陆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I would recommend a large well-armed landing party.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.69,0:01:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,但是现在这种情况，我们去的人越多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, but in this case, with the more people we take down,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.40,0:01:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,就越有可能触犯他们的某条禁忌\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the greater chance we have of violating one of their taboos.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.99,0:01:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,同意，一旦他们认为我们是来炫耀武力的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Agreed. Once they've got it into their heads we're showing force,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.58,0:01:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,就不会再记得什么采矿协议了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}you can forget them signing any mining treaty.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.04,0:01:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,很好，史考特，你来指挥\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Very well. Scotty, you're in command.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.62,0:01:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,记住，这一区域曾观察到有克林贡人出没\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bear in mind that the Klingons have been sighted in this sector.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.46,0:01:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我们去下面谈判的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}While we're negotiating there, we don't want the Enterprise
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.21,0:01:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- 可不希望进取号出什么问题 - 是，舰长，我们会保持警惕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- to become an incident up here. - Aye, sir. We'll keep on our toes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.08,0:01:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,站住！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Halt!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.00,0:02:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你们是从地球来的？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You are of the Earth vessel?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.92,0:02:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我是寇克舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am Captain Kirk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.09,0:02:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我们手无寸铁，为和平而来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We come with open hearts and hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.81,0:02:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- 克林贡人！ - 格兰特，别！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- A Klingon! - Grant, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.78,0:02:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,宇宙，最后的边疆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Space, the final frontier.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.75,0:02:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这是星舰进取号的航程\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}These are the voyages of the starship Enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.96,0:02:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,它的五年任务，是去探索未知的新世界\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Its five-year mission: To explore strange new worlds,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.01,0:02:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,找寻新的生命与新的文明\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to seek out new life and new civilizations,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.14,0:02:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,勇敢的航向前人未至之境\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to boldly go where no man has gone before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.61,0:03:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,【星际迷航：原初】
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.12,0:03:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,-=THE LAST FANTASY=-\N荣誉出品\N本字幕仅供学习交流，严禁用于商业途径
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.63,0:03:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&}-=TLF字幕组=-\N翻译：诺阿诺阿\N校对：喜马拉雅{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.27,0:03:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,第二季第十一集\N「星期五的孩子」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.99,0:03:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长日志，星历3497.2\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain's log, stardate 3497.2.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.32,0:03:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,科普兰IV星球\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Planet Capella IV.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.08,0:03:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里发现了大量托帕林\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The rare mineral topaline
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.95,0:03:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一种对小行星殖民地生命维持系统\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}vital to the life support systems of planetoid colonies
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.96,0:03:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,至关重要的稀有矿物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}has been discovered in abundance here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.33,0:03:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的任务是，争取达成采矿协议\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Our mission: Obtain a mining agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.42,0:03:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我们发现有一名克林贡特工捷足先登\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But we've discovered a Klingon agent has preceded us to the planet,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.13,0:03:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这一发现导致我们一名船员牺牲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}a discovery which has cost the life of one of my crewmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.14,0:04:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道我们之间有任何战争，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am unaware of any state of war between our peoples, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.60,0:04:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,吉姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.93,0:04:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,还是说你们有规定要杀死任何视线内的克林贡人？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Or is it your policy to kill Klingons on sight?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.03,0:04:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他还很年轻…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He was young...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.86,0:04:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,…经验不足\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...and inexperienced.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.66,0:04:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,马布知道克林贡人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Does Maab know that the Klingons are our sworn enemies
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.87,0:04:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,是我们的死敌吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}by their own words?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.46,0:04:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我们只知道他们也愿意花大价钱换我们的石头\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We understand only that he also offers things of value for our rocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.04,0:04:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,而且还把自己的武器和其他设备交给了我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And he has freely handed us his weapons and other devices.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.80,0:04:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你们也会这么做吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Will you do the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.68,0:04:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,让我联系我的星舰，通知他们…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let me call my ship and inform them...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.39,0:04:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,攻击我们的村庄？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}To bring down an attack upon their village?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.15,0:04:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉过你，马布\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It is as I told you, Maab.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.90,0:04:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,地球人害怕诚实的讨价还价\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Earthmen fear to bargain honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.57,0:04:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你们会把武器交出来吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Will you hand us your weapons?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.93,0:05:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,他们非常守信，尤其诚实\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"So they keep their word scrupulously. They're unusually honest."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.27,0:05:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,在会议室时你是这么说的吧，医生？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is that what I heard you say in the Briefing Room, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.28,0:05:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,是，我提到过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, I mentioned that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.86,0:05:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他也提到过他们会非常危险\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He also mentioned that they can be highly dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.95,0:05:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,如果对他们撒谎的话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dangerous if lied to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.91,0:05:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,如果违反他们的习俗的话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If their customs are violated.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.62,0:05:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我们没有撒谎，也没有违反他们的习俗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, we lied to no one, Doctor. We violated no customs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.79,0:05:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你来跟我解释一下，为什么我的船员死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Perhaps you'll explain to me why one of my men is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.12,0:05:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他拿武器指着对方的另一位客人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Because he was drawing a weapon on another of their guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.96,0:05:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,格兰特抬头\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Grant looked up,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.46,0:05:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,看见一个克林贡人，作出了完全出于本能的行为\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}saw a Klingon, made a purely instinctive defensive move.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.64,0:05:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,克林贡人在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What's a Klingon doing down here
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.43,0:06:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你那十分诚实守信的朋友这里做什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}among your scrupulously honest friends anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.64,0:06:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,吉姆，我知道失去一名船员你很难过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Look, Jim, I know what it means to you to lose a crewman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.36,0:06:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,这里只有一名\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's only one down, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.15,0:06:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,还有400多名船员在轨道上的星舰里呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's over 400 more up there in orbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.82,0:06:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,如果这里有一名克林贡人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And if there's a Klingon down here...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.16,0:06:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那肯定某处有一艘克林贡人的飞船\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...there might be a Klingon ship up there somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.83,0:06:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,史考特先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Scott...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.21,0:06:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,传感器上有东西出现了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...picking up something on the sensors, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.51,0:06:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来像一艘飞船\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Seems to be another ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.13,0:06:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,放到显示器上看看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let's put it on the screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.18,0:06:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,就在我们传感器扫描范围的边缘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's just at the edge of our sensor range, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.69,0:06:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,很难得到精确读数\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hard to get an exact reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.35,0:06:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得是克林贡飞船？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You think it's a Klingon ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.94,0:06:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,谁还会跟星舰玩捉迷藏呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Who else would be playing cat and mouse with a starship?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.87,0:07:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,距离太远，它也奈何不了我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can't hurt us much out there, bobbing about like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.95,0:07:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,先不着急呼叫舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No need to call the captain yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.56,0:07:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,老骨头\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.98,0:07:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.52,0:07:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我不应该责骂你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I shouldn't have chewed you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.27,0:07:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.28,0:07:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我理解\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.24,0:07:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,然而，这样没有效率\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Inefficient, however.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.24,0:07:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,感情用事，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Emotion, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.33,0:07:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你说的很对，史波克先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, you're quite right, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.58,0:07:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,无效…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Inefficient...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.71,0:07:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,…且不合逻辑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...and illogical.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.30,0:08:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你交出了武器，显示了我们的友好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You've shown friendship by handing over our weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.52,0:08:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,她现在也作出相同的姿态\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And she's making a gesture in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.69,0:08:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,吉姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.45,0:08:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你碰了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If you touch it,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.12,0:08:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,她最近的男性亲属就要杀了你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}her nearest male relative will have to try to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.99,0:08:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,他们这是给你战斗的机会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They're offering you a chance for combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.00,0:08:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,他们认为战斗比爱更具乐趣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They consider it more pleasurable than love.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.47,0:08:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你表现的很失落，他们就会满意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It would appear, captain, that he finds you a disappointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.78,0:08:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我是阿卡王，提尔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am the Teer, Akaar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.74,0:09:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,领导科普兰的十个部落\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I lead the Ten Tribes of Capella.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.34,0:09:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这是依琳\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And this is Eleen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.46,0:09:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我年轻的妻子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A young wife,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.09,0:09:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,即将诞下我的子嗣，延续我的统治\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to give an old man a son to rule these tribes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.47,0:09:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我是寇克舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm Captain Kirk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.68,0:09:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,首先，我必须对我手下船员的死亡表示抗议\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}First, I must protest the killing of one of my crewmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.02,0:09:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那是你的船员，为你而死不是他的荣幸吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If it was your man, was it not his privilege to die for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.85,0:09:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我不理解 - 他们的风俗和我们不同，提尔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I do not understand. - Their customs are different, Teer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.36,0:09:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,也和我们的不同，提尔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And different from those of my people too, Teer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.86,0:09:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,他们惧怕死亡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The sight of death frightens them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.86,0:09:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,让我来，吉姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let me take this, Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.78,0:09:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,马布说的没错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What Maab has said is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.50,0:09:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的风俗不同\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Our customs are different.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.83,0:09:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,克林贡人所说的不重要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What the Klingon has said is unimportant,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.34,0:09:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不愿听他所说的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and we do not hear his words.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.13,0:09:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚才说克林贡人是骗子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I just called the Klingon a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.72,0:09:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,可笑吗，提尔？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Laughter, Teer?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.22,0:10:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,克林贡人不也是我们尊贵的客人？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is not the Klingon an honoured guest also?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.97,0:10:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,地球人是第一个出价购买我们的石头的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It is the Earth people who first bargained for our rocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.31,0:10:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,对我们来说，难道不是两方出价购买同样的东西更好吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is it not best to have two who bargain for the same goods?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.73,0:10:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我代表部落发言，马布 - 我代表多数人发言，提尔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- It is I who speak for the tribe, Maab. - I speak for many, Teer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.57,0:10:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,听听克林贡人怎么说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hear the words of the Klingon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.58,0:10:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,地球人向你们提供什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What do Earthmen offer you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.87,0:10:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,过去你们从他们那里得到了什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What have you obtained from them in the past?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.29,0:10:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,治疗疾病的粉末和药水？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Powders and liquids for the sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.92,0:10:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,克林贡人和你们一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We Klingons believe as you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.63,0:10:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,都认为生病的人就应该死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The sick should die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.80,0:10:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,只有强者才能生存\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Only the strong should live.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.06,0:10:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,地球人承诺教授你们部落的年轻人很多东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Earthmen have promised to teach the youth of your tribes many things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.19,0:10:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那么究竟是什么东西？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What? What things?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.61,0:10:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,抵御敌人的小聪明？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Cleverness against enemies?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.44,0:10:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 如何使用武器？ - 克林贡人说的没错，阿卡王\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- The use of weapons? - The Klingon speaks the truth, Akaar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.37,0:11:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,地球联盟还提供了另外一样东西，阿卡王\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The Earth Federation offers one other thing, Akaar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.75,0:11:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的律法，我们律法中的最高原则是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Our laws. And the highest of all our laws states:
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.55,0:11:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你们的世界，一直都是你们的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your world is yours, and will always remain yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.80,0:11:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我们和克林贡人不同的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This differs us from the Klingons.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.56,0:11:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,他们的帝国因征服世界而组成\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Their empire is made up of conquered worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.10,0:11:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,他们用军队和武力夺走想要的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They take what they want by arms and force.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.19,0:11:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.65,0:11:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,就让克林贡人和地球人在这里娱乐大家吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let the Klingons and the Earthmen offer us amusement.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.90,0:11:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,科普兰人喜欢这些\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Capellans welcome this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.44,0:11:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,地球人的风俗与我们不同\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The Earthmen have different customs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.74,0:11:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,但是他们从来没对我们撒谎过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But never have they lied to our people.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.82,0:11:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有些人不愿与地球人做交易，阿卡王\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There are those of us who will not bargain with Earthmen, Akaar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.46,0:11:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你这是要挑战我吗，马布？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you say you will fight me, Maab?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.59,0:11:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,您来选，提尔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let that be your choice, Teer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.36,0:12:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要通讯设备\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We need our communicators, those devices on our belts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.40,0:12:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,如果这附近有克林贡人的飞船…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If there's a Klingon ship somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.49,0:12:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不关心天空\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The sky does not interest me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.66,0:12:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我要考虑一番\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I must consider the words I have heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.71,0:12:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,退下吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Leave him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.06,0:12:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那艘飞船消失了，超出范围了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The ship's disappeared, sir. Gone out of range.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.90,0:12:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,史考特先生，我收到来自一艘飞船的呼叫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Scott, I'm getting a call from a vessel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.07,0:12:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,信号很弱，无法辨认\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So faint I can't make it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.99,0:12:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,用放大器试一下，看能不能捕捉到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Put a booster on it, Lieutenant. Try to pull it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.41,0:13:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,没有了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've lost it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.46,0:13:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉像是来自地球飞船的求救信号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It sounded like a distress signal from an Earth vessel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.27,0:13:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,克林贡人！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Klingon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.98,0:14:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,通讯设备，还有武器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Communicators. Weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.89,0:14:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我和你们没有争端，舰长，只是希望…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I have no quarrel with you, captain. I wish merely to...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.61,0:14:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,返回我们的飞船\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...return to my vessel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.66,0:14:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,飞船类型是什么？位置在哪里？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Type of vessel? Location?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.28,0:14:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,一艘小型侦查船，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A small scout ship, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.75,0:14:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也需要矿物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We need the mineral too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.37,0:14:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我是被派来谈判的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was sent to negotiate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.92,0:14:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,放开他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Release him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.02,0:14:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,阿卡已经死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Akaar is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.69,0:14:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我是提尔王\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am the Teer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.69,0:14:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- 杀了他们 - 等等！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Kill them now. - Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.95,0:14:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你做人们的领袖，一定要做出正确的选择\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If you lead these people now, be certain you make the right decisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.21,0:15:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,十个部落的新领袖怕了吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is the new leader of the Ten Tribes afraid?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.00,0:15:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- 让我帮你杀了他们 - 或者让我和克林贡人决斗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Let me kill them for you. - Or let the Klingon and me fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.38,0:15:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你就当看热闹了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It might amuse you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.93,0:15:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,也许，作为提尔王就是要用新眼光看待事物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Perhaps to be a Teer is to see in new ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.81,0:15:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我开始喜欢你了，地球人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I begin to like you, Earthman.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.23,0:15:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我在克林贡人的眼里看到了恐惧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And I saw fear in the Klingon's eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.40,0:15:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有协议的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We had an agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.41,0:15:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,协议也可以变，克林贡人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That too, may change, Klingon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.50,0:15:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,史考特先生，可以收到清晰信号了 是求救信号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I have the signal clear now, Mr. Scott. It is a distress call.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.58,0:15:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,来自迪尔德丽号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's from the SS Dierdre.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.17,0:15:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,迪尔德丽号是运输舰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dierdre. That's a freighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.88,0:15:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,他们遭到了攻击，在逃跑，试图想办法摆脱敌人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Reporting they're under attack. They're running, trying to manoeuvre.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.26,0:15:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是克林贡人飞船在攻击他们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's a Klingon vessel attacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.02,0:16:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 荷尔姆？ - 收到，长官，正在修改航向\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Helm? - Picking it up, sir. Taking a fix.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.73,0:16:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,呼叫舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Try the captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.69,0:16:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,进取号呼叫寇克舰长，收到请回答\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Enterprise to Captain Kirk. Come in, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.61,0:16:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,进取号呼叫寇克舰长，收到请回答\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Enterprise to Captain Kirk. Come in, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.54,0:16:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，小心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.55,0:16:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你怀的孩子会成为提尔王 - 我难逃一死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- You carry a child who would be Teer. - I must die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.56,0:16:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.55,0:17:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,男人不可触碰提尔王的妻子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No man may touch the wife of a Teer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.02,0:17:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,她准备好受死了，地球人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She was prepared to die, Earthman.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.36,0:17:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直为自己遵守法律而骄傲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was proud to obey the laws.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.53,0:17:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,先杀了他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Kill him first.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.07,0:17:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他碰了我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He laid hands upon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.99,0:17:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我有权看着他死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It is my right to see him die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.83,0:17:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,进取号呼叫史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Enterprise to Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.71,0:17:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,麦考伊医生，请回答\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dr. McCoy, come in please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.05,0:17:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,传感器上可以看到，上尉，传送到我的频道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I have it on the sensors, sir. Tie into my channel, lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.85,0:17:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,已传送\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tied in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.06,0:18:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,…我们遭到了来自克林贡飞船的猛烈攻击\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}... commanding. We are under heavy attack by Klingon vessels.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.23,0:18:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,两艘护卫舰已损毁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Two convoy ships are already damaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.56,0:18:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,请务必提供援助，进取号，收到请回复\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We must have help. Enterprise, acknowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.48,0:18:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,收到请回复…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Please acknowledge. Repeat...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.24,0:18:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,已重新计算拦截航线并导入，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Interception course computed and laid in, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.62,0:18:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,准备驶离轨道，苏鲁先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Prepare to take us out of orbit, Mr. Sulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.67,0:18:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,是，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Aye, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.43,0:18:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,史考特，舰长还…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Scotty, the captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.51,0:18:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,有一艘联邦星舰遭到了攻击，向我们发出求救信号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We have a distress call from a Federation ship under attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.14,0:18:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我们的职责所在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's where our duty lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.27,0:18:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,苏鲁，驶离轨道，曲速5前进\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Take us out of orbit, Mr. Sulu. Ahead warp 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.37,0:19:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长日志，星历3498.9\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain's log, stardate 3498.9.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.95,0:19:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,史考特少校暂任指挥官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lieutenant Commander Scott in temporary command.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.79,0:19:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我们被迫离开科普兰星球，前去营救一艘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We were forced to leave Capella to come to the aid of a Federation vessel
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.25,0:19:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,正遭受克林贡人攻击的联邦星舰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}under attack by a Klingon vessel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.68,0:19:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,回应求救信号之前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We were unable to contact our landing party
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.31,0:19:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我们无法与地面派遣小组取得联系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}before we were forced to answer the distress signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.73,0:19:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,无法与地面派遣小组取得联系很是蹊跷\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Our inability to reach the landing party is strange,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.52,0:19:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我很担心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and I am concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.40,0:19:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的回舰信号已经发出1小时12分钟了，还没有回复…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Our check-in signal is one hour 12 minutes overdue.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.32,0:19:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,鉴于没有侦察小组出现\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Since no reconnaissance party has appeared,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.33,0:19:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,鉴于史考特先生在这方面总是十分高效…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and since Mr. Scott is notably efficient in such matters...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.17,0:19:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,可以确定一定是有什么事让他抽不开身\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I must assume that something's keeping them busy up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.88,0:19:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,克林贡飞船\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The Klingon ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.96,0:19:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这个结论很合理\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That would seem a logical conclusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.76,0:19:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.72,0:20:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我得治好那女人的胳膊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...l'm gonna fix that woman's arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.47,0:20:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我碰了她，他们也只能杀我一次\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They can only kill me once for touching her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.61,0:20:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好主意，老骨头\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's a very good idea, Bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.53,0:20:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,没错，舰长，这主意很棒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, captain. An excellent idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.08,0:20:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看看那只胳膊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let me see that arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.58,0:20:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能碰我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You will not touch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.72,0:20:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你之前说自己准备好赴死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You said you were prepared to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.26,0:20:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,难道说你更愿意活着？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Does that mean you prefer to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.60,0:20:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,回到星舰我们就可以保证你的安全，少校你自己来选\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I think we can get you safely to the ship. Your choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.90,0:20:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,活着总是更吸引人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}To live is always desirable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.95,0:20:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,很好，走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All right, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.25,0:21:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,克林贡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Klingon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.18,0:21:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那边没什么需要你担心的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There is nothing to concern you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.39,0:21:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有协议，马布，我有权掌握自己的武器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We made an agreement, Maab. I have a right to my weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.78,0:21:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会好好保管的，克林贡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We have them well cared for, Klingon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.49,0:21:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,等我们的生意谈妥了，就会还给你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your weapon will be returned when our business is completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.20,0:21:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,这才是我们的协议\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That was our agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.33,0:21:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,后部相位炮已准备好，即将进入舰桥\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Aft phaser, affirmative. We're going to bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.83,0:21:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,接近运输舰的最后报告位置，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Approaching the freighter's last reported position, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.83,0:21:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,传感器报告，契诃夫？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sensor report, Mr. Chekov?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.00,0:21:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,没有，长官，没有残骸，没有遗留物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Negative, sir. No debris, no residual particles.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.47,0:21:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,毫无痕迹\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No traces.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.68,0:21:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,苏鲁先生，启动标准搜索程序\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Sulu, begin a standard search pattern.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.85,0:21:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,开启全部扫描仪，契诃夫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All scanners full intensity, Mr. Chekov.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.06,0:22:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没有信号？ - 没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- No signal at all? - Negative, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.02,0:22:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,现在应该已经在显示器上了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It should be on our screens by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.15,0:22:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,运输舰的最大速度不过曲速2\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}At best a freighter might travel warp two.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.11,0:22:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我很清楚运输舰的最大速度，苏鲁先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm well aware of a freighter's maximum speed, Mr. Sulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.50,0:22:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长日志，星历3499.1\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain's log, stardate 3499.1.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.00,0:22:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,离开科普兰营地之前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Before leaving the Capellan encampment,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.17,0:22:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我们设法拿到了通讯设备\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}we managed to retrieve our communicators.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.80,0:22:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,但是没有找到相位枪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Our phasers were not to be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.71,0:22:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我们逃到了山丘地带，但是科普兰人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We have fled into the hills, yet we know the Capellans will eventually find us
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.55,0:22:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,最终根据气味会找到我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}by scent alone, if necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.93,0:22:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我们知道了另外一件事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And we have learned one thing more.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.89,0:22:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这个叫伊莲的女孩，恨她腹中未出生的孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The girl, Eleen, hates the unborn child she is carrying.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.85,0:22:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,老骨头，陪着她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Stay with her, Bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.82,0:22:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,真是个瓮中捉鳖的好地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Nice place to get trapped in.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.11,0:22:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,但是也易守难攻啊，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But a defensible entrance, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.66,0:23:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.83,0:23:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,去看看那条路，看能不能找到出口\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Scout up the trail that way. See what we have in the way of an exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.42,0:23:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我查看一下周围环境\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll take a look around.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.01,0:23:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,听我说，就算你是科普兰女人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now listen, you may be a Capellan woman
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.05,0:23:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,就算你是提尔王的妻子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and the widow of a High Teer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.09,0:23:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,但我是医生，救死扶伤是我的职责\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But I'm a doctor, and it's my tradition to care for the sick and injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.77,0:23:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看看你的胳膊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now let me see that arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.86,0:24:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你不能这么碰我 - 你给我听好了，年轻的女士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- You will not touch me in that manner. - Now you listen to me, young woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.49,0:24:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我的专业判断需要我怎么碰你，我就怎么碰你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll touch you in any way or manner that my professional judgement indicates.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.52,0:24:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我想的一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.85,0:24:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,随时可能分娩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It can come any time now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.94,0:24:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.78,0:24:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我是医生，怎么会不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Because I'm a doctor, that's how I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.28,0:24:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,村子里的女人都不可能碰一下就知道这么多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Even the women of our village cannot tell so much with a touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.12,0:25:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,真是只奇怪的手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Strange hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.00,0:25:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这么柔软\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Very soft.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.90,0:25:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,山石越来越高，山路越来越窄，但是有条路可以出去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The walls get higher and narrower, but there is a way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.07,0:25:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.45,0:25:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,要是等堵住入口，可以争取更多时间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If we could block off that entrance, it'd give us more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.07,0:25:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他们得绕过这些山 - 这里的石头还有页岩很松\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- They'd have to go around these hills. - There's enough loose rock and shale.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.74,0:25:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以用两台通讯设备\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you think we could create a sonic disruption
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.08,0:25:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,造成音波破坏\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}with two of our communicators?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.79,0:25:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,成功的几率很小\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Only a very slight chance it would work.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.08,0:25:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,要是你觉得不行，那就别试了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, if you don't think we can, maybe we shouldn't try.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.30,0:25:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有这么说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I didn't say that exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.11,0:26:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,声波束会使那边山石的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sound beams should produce a sympathetic vibration...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.29,0:26:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,疏松区域产生共振\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...on the weak area of that slide.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.89,0:28:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,担心会随时分娩？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Worried about the delivery?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.06,0:28:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,科普兰人不是人类，吉姆，他们是类人物种\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Capellans aren't human, Jim. They're humanoid.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.15,0:28:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,身体内部构造是有区别的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There are certain internal differences.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.98,0:28:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有应付紧急情况所需的工具\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't have the equipment to handle an emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.28,0:28:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你要是觉得自己不行… - 算了，我可以的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- If you don't think you can handle it... - Forget it. I can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.40,0:28:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,最不需要的就是身边有个笨手笨脚的舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The last thing I want around is a ham-handed ship's captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.09,0:29:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不行！只有麦考伊可以\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No! Only McCoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.26,0:29:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那边有个洞，可能是这附近唯一的庇护\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's a cave in there. Probably the only shelter around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.26,0:29:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要人帮我扶着她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll need help getting her in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.52,0:29:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不行！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.98,0:29:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我是医生，不是自动扶梯，史波克，帮帮我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Look, I'm a doctor, not an escalator. Spock! Give me a hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.23,0:29:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我只允许你碰我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I will allow only your touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.09,0:30:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,飞船不会无故消失\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A vessel doesn't just disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.10,0:30:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,什么都没有，史考特先生 所有频道所有频率都试过了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's nothing, Mr. Scott. All channels and frequencies are clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.10,0:30:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,契诃夫先生？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Chekov?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.69,0:30:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,什么都没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Nothing, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.19,0:30:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是被摧毁了，肯定能够发现残骸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If it were destroyed, I'd pick up debris readings of some sort.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.46,0:30:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,也不可能超过我们，毕竟是艘运输舰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It couldn't have run away from us, sir. Not a freighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.67,0:30:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,契诃夫先生，再放一遍求救信号的带子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Chekov, pull the microtape on that distress call. I want it replayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.06,0:30:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,…我们遭到了克林贡飞船的攻击\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}... commanding. We are under heavy attack by Klingon vessels.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.48,0:30:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,两艘护卫舰已损毁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Two convoy ships are already damaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.78,0:31:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,请务必援助，进取号，收到请回复\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We must have help! Enterprise, acknowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.65,0:31:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- 收到请回复 - 听到了吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Please acknowledge. - Did you hear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.16,0:31:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,它指明了我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They called us by name.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.78,0:31:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不是一般的求救信号，而是针对我们的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not a general distress signal, but one aimed right at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.96,0:31:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,一般都会向最近的星舰求救\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Wouldn't they normally call for the nearest starship?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.67,0:31:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,一艘运输舰怎么会知道我们在这一区域执行任务？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How would a freighter know we were ordered into this sector?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.42,0:31:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,陷阱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.38,0:31:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,调虎离山\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We were diverted from the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.56,0:31:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,也可能真的是求救信号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Or it could be an authentic distress call.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.73,0:31:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会搞清楚的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We'll stay long enough to make certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.15,0:31:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 继续搜索程序 - 是，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Continue search pattern. - Yes, sir. Continuing.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.46,0:31:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,老骨头？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bones?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.12,0:31:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你的工具袋里还有硝酸菱镁片吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You've got one of those magnesite-nitron tablets in your kit.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.88,0:31:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- 给我一个 - 等一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Give me one. - Just a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.25,0:31:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我先让她坐下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let me get her on the rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.28,0:32:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这里疼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Pain is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.66,0:32:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你是怎么可以碰她的？给她吃镇定剂了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How did you arrange to touch her, Bones? Give her a happy pill?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.21,0:32:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不是，用右吊拳\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No. Right cross.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.21,0:32:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- 医典里面可没写这个啊 - 从此以后就写在我的医典里了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Never seen that in a medical book. - It's in mine from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.60,0:32:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不是，在那里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, it's there.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.40,0:32:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那里疼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Pain is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.74,0:33:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,植物，舰长，看来附近有水\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Vegetation, captain. Evidently there's water nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.95,0:33:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,很好，但是我们还需要武器，就像需要水一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Good. But we need weapons just as much as we need water, Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.16,0:33:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,很快就会有武器了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There would seem to be little weapon potential at hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.13,0:33:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.09,0:33:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,麦考伊！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}McCoy!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.89,0:33:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,别怕，我在这儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Easy. I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.64,0:33:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你得要这个孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You must want the child.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.98,0:33:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.86,0:33:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里，孩子属于丈夫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Here child belongs to husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.16,0:33:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这么说什么都是他们的，明摆着的！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So they take all the credit here. Poppycock!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.66,0:33:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我，你想让我帮你吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Answer me. Do you want my help?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.13,0:33:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我，你想让我帮你吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Answer me. Do you want my help?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.13,0:34:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.14,0:34:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉自己，“这孩子是我的”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Say to yourself, "The child is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.35,0:34:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这孩子是我的，是我的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The child is mine. It is mine."
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.98,0:34:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,没错，是你的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes. It's yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.35,0:34:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不是，不是这样的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No. You've got it all wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.23,0:34:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,没错，麦考伊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, McCoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.53,0:34:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是你的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.91,0:34:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不是，你要对自己说，“这孩子是我的”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No. Say to yourself, "The child is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.87,0:34:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是我的，是…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It is mine. It is..."
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.14,0:34:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,寇克呼叫进取号，请回答\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Kirk to Enterprise. Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.56,0:34:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,寇克呼叫进取号，请回答\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Kirk to Enterprise. Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.65,0:35:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,幸好这树皮拉伸聚合性很好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Fortunately this bark has suitable tensile cohesion.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.82,0:35:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说做弓弦很合适？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You mean it makes a good bow string?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.24,0:35:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是这么说的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I believe I said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.00,0:35:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这才像话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's more like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.05,0:35:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,既然科普兰人不会做弓箭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Since the Capellans never developed the bow,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.59,0:35:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,这会让他们大吃一惊的，就像地球上的火药一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}this may come as big a surprise as gunpowder was on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.93,0:36:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不对，史波克，这样不对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, Mr. Spock. That isn't the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.76,0:36:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这只胳膊放下面，支撑背部\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You place this arm under here to support its back,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.14,0:36:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这只放这里，抱住头部\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and this hand here, to support its head.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.10,0:36:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我还是算了吧，谢谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I would rather not, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.98,0:36:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,麦考伊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}McCoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.07,0:36:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,把我们的孩子抱过来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bring our child.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.61,0:36:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,“我们的”孩子？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"Our" child?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.66,0:36:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我待会儿解释？ - 估计会很有意思\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I'll explain later. - That should prove very interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.65,0:36:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,还是没有，史考特先生，干干净净\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Still negative, Mr. Scott. All sweeps.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.90,0:36:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- 契诃夫先生？ - 什么都没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Mr. Chekov? - Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.19,0:36:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- 准备返回，曲速5，舵手 - 曲速5，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- We're turning back. Warp five, helm. - Warp five, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.83,0:37:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,返回科普兰IV\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}On course for Capella IV.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.37,0:37:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,如果可以的话，提速到曲速6\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Warp 6 as soon as she'll take it, Mr. Sulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.37,0:37:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长可能有麻烦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The captain could be in trouble back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.09,0:37:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,史考特先生，收到来自联邦星舰卡罗莱纳号的求救信号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Scott. Another distress call from the USS Carolina.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.59,0:37:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,忽略它\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ignore it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.80,0:37:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,史考特先生，卡罗莱纳号确实是在这一区域登记的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Scott, the Carolina is registered in this sector.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.43,0:37:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,忽略它，上尉，有问题我来负责\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ignore it, lieutenant. Log it as my order, my responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.51,0:37:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,是，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Aye, aye, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.22,0:37:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,史考特，万一是真的…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Scotty, if it should turn out to be real...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.39,0:37:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,地球上有句俗话，苏鲁先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's an old, old saying on Earth, Mr. Sulu:
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.35,0:37:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,“骗我一次，你可耻，骗我两次，是我笨”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"Fool me once, shame on you. Fool me twice, shame on me."
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.40,0:37:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我听过，这句话源自俄罗斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know this saying. It was invented in Russia.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.63,0:38:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,吉姆！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Jim!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.79,0:38:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Spock!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.47,0:38:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,吉姆！史波克！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Jim! Spock!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.97,0:38:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了，老骨头？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What happened, Bones?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.60,0:38:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我的病人用石头砸晕我，自己跑了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My patient spattered me with a rock. She's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.73,0:38:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- 孩子呢？ - 他很好，这这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- The child? - It's all right. It's in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.31,0:38:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,看来我忘记了精神疗法，只关注了手术\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I guess I'll forget psychiatry, stick with surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.28,0:38:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我真的以为她是真心想要 - 美德是一个相对的概念，医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I really thought she'd learn to want it. - Virtue is a relative term, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.91,0:39:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- 她会直接去找那些战士 - 我和你一起去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- She'll head straight to the warriors. - I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.58,0:39:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,早在登上进取号之前你就已经发下了医德誓言\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You took a medical oath long before you signed aboard my ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.50,0:39:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那里还有个小病人需要你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That small patient in there needs you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.26,0:39:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- 评估一下这个星球？ - 31分钟，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Estimating the planet? - Thirty-one minutes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.64,0:39:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,扫描仪呼叫舰桥，请讲，引擎控制\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Scanner to Bridge. Read. Engineering control.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.27,0:39:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,史考特先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Scott.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.24,0:39:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,传感器上显示有飞船朝我们的方向飞来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sensors picking up a vessel ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.49,0:39:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,挡住了我们的去路\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Cutting across our path.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.28,0:39:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 亚光速前进 - 调整至一半光速\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Sub-light, one half. - Reversing to sub-light. One half.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.71,0:39:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是外星人，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's an alien, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.29,0:39:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,据分析，是一艘克林贡战舰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}By configuration, a Klingon warship.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.01,0:39:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,正朝我们的方向来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Taking position directly in our path.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.72,0:40:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- 苏鲁，发出战斗警报 - 是，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Mr. Sulu, sound battle stations. - Aye, aye, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.05,0:40:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,联邦星舰进取号呼叫克林贡飞船，请回答\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is the USS Enterprise calling unidentified Klingon vessel. Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.52,0:40:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,联邦星舰进取号呼叫克林贡飞船，收到请回答\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}USS Enterprise calling Klingon vessel. Acknowledge, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.53,0:40:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,屏幕上可以看到了，长官，还很远\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I have it on the viewscreen now, sir. Still distant.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.08,0:40:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,位于我们的正前方，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Holding a position dead ahead, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.83,0:40:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,划清界限，警告对方不要越过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Drawing a line, daring us to step over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.04,0:40:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,还在接近\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Still closing.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.21,0:40:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,对方直接朝我们的航线飞来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The alien is directly in our line of flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.59,0:41:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我是联邦星舰进取号的指挥官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is the commander of the USS Enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.56,0:41:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,亮明你方身份及目的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Identify yourself and your intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.23,0:41:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,完毕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Acknowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.61,0:41:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,关掉频率，上尉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Close out the frequency, lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.86,0:41:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,相位炮准备就绪，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Phaser banks are ready, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.11,0:41:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,如果有必要，我们就直捣对方心脏\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And we'll go right down their throat, if necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.83,0:41:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,看看他们胆量\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let's see if they have the belly for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.26,0:42:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,在上面的石头后面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Behind the rocks up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.26,0:42:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,地球人很会玩游戏\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The Earthmen make excellent game.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.31,0:42:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,他们的聪明让我惊讶\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Their cleverness has surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.68,0:42:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,他们非死不可\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They must die.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.10,0:42:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你们的律法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That is your law.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.65,0:42:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我们尊崇自己的法律，也会信守诺言，克林贡人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We will honour our law and our word to you, Klingon.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.78,0:42:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,马布\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Maab.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.80,0:42:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那孩子死了，马布\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The child is dead, Maab.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.81,0:43:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,正如我也会死在你手里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do as you will with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.43,0:43:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,地球人呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The Earthmen?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.60,0:43:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.94,0:43:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我趁他们睡觉时杀了他们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I killed them as they slept.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.44,0:43:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你说的是真的，带我们去看看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If true, take us to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.87,0:43:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你怀疑我，克林贡人？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you doubt my word, Klingon?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.04,0:43:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我是提尔王之妻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am the wife of a Teer.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.66,0:43:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我会死在自己的帐篷里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I will die in my own tent.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.21,0:43:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这合乎规矩，她的确是提尔王之妻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It is in order. She is the wife of a Teer.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.05,0:43:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不行！我们要先证实她的话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No! First we verify her story!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.56,0:43:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是你所说的信守诺言吗，克林贡人？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is this what your sworn word means, Klingon?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.47,0:44:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Spock?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.81,0:44:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这里，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Here, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.78,0:44:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这边，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Over here, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.45,0:44:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克呼叫进取号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Spock to Enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.79,0:44:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不会再有千钧一发时突然出现的骑兵了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The cavalry doesn't come over the hill in the nick of time any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.54,0:44:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你是说我们没法指望进取号的支援，我同意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If by that you mean we can't expect help from the Enterprise, I must agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.64,0:45:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我只想要一样东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's just one thing I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.81,0:45:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,克林贡人？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The Klingon?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.73,0:45:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我们中有一人得抓住他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}One of us must get him.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.81,0:45:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,复仇吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Revenge, captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.98,0:45:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,有何不可？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.28,0:45:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,再有人敢拿起武器，你们全都必死无疑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The next man who raises a weapon destroys all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.82,0:45:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你们，还有你们的原始武器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You and your primitive knives and your weapons!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.99,0:45:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我会让你们见识见识什么是真正的杀戮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll teach you what killing really means.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.91,0:45:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,克林贡！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Klingon!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.71,0:45:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,打啊！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.42,0:45:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你们是战士还是孩子？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are you warriors or children?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.34,0:45:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,马布，我会逃走的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Maab. I will flee.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.01,0:45:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,等到克林贡人开火的时候，我会…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}When the Klingon turns to fire, I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.81,0:45:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,身为十个部落的提尔王，我赦免你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}As Teer of the Ten Tribes, I give you back your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.90,0:45:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,而我的生命到此为止\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mine is now forfeit.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.19,0:45:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,基尔，准备好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Keel, stand ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.87,0:46:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,克林贡人！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Klingon!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.85,0:47:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,别动！放下武器！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hold it there! Drop your weapons!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.21,0:47:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我们很想念你，史考特先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We missed you, Mr. Scott.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.54,0:47:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我们去追了一下克林贡飞船\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We had a wee bit of a run-in with a Klingon vessel
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.63,0:47:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,但是无意恋战\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but he had no stomach for fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.21,0:47:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我们检查过营地，发现你们在那里逗留过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We checked the encampment, found out you were here
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.67,0:47:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,然后就一路追到了这里，我可以…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and had no trouble at all in tracking you down. I could...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.68,0:47:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不对，不是这样抱的，像这样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, that's not the way to handle it. Here, like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.64,0:47:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这只手抱住头部\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Here, take its little head like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.85,0:47:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,胳膊放下面，就这样，很容易吧？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There. Arm under, that's it. See how easy?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.82,0:47:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,“呜哧呜哧呜哧”？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"Oochy-woochy-kootchy-coo," captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.99,0:47:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,一种很晦涩的地球方言，史波克先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}An obscure Earth dialect, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.33,0:48:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,想知道的话可以查查语言学相关著作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If you're curious, consult linguistics.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.33,0:48:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,想来会很有意思\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}At any rate, this should prove interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.33,0:48:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,有意思？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.54,0:48:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那女人开始解释新的提尔王\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}When the woman starts explaining how the new High Teer
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.17,0:48:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会是麦考伊医生的孩子的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}is actually Dr. McCoy's child.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.17,0:48:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,什么，史波克先生？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What's that again, Mr. Spock?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.55,0:48:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也不是很懂自己，史考特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We don't actually understand it ourselves, Mr. Scott.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.05,0:48:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,麦考伊也不懂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Nor does Dr. McCoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.02,0:48:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,联络星际舰队\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Contact Starfleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.65,0:48:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,通知他们星际联邦在科普兰星的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Inform them that Federation mining rights on Capella
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.07,0:48:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,采矿权已有协议保障\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}have been secured by treaty.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.57,0:48:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,文件已由新首领的摄政王签署\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Documents signed by the young High Chief's regent.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.16,0:48:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- 详细报告稍后发回 - 是，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Report follows. - Aye, aye, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.70,0:48:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- 摄政王？ - 没错，伊莲，一位了不起的年轻女士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- The child's regent? - Yes. Eleen. A remarkable young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.67,0:48:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,代表新的提尔王\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Representing the High Teer,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.21,0:48:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,伦纳德·詹姆士·阿卡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Leonard James Akaar.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.26,0:48:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那孩子叫做伦纳德·詹姆士·阿卡？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The child was named Leonard James Akaar?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.68,0:48:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,朗朗上口，对吧，詹姆士？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Has a kind of a ring to it, don't you think, James?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.56,0:49:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得这名字会名垂青史，伦纳德\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I think it's a name destined to go down in galactic history, Leonard.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.48,0:49:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你觉得怎么样，史波克？ - 我觉得这个事情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- What do you think, Spock? - I think you're both gonna be
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.89,0:49:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,可以让两位开心至少一个月，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}insufferably pleased with yourselves for at least a month, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.36,0:49:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,驶离轨道，苏鲁先生，以曲速一前进\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Take us out of orbit, Mr. Sulu. Ahead, warp factor one.
